Found a question on Blind where someone was asked to "Compress an image represented as a 2D matrix." and the candidate got confused and was not able to answer below is one of the answer I can think of
SInce it is a very generic question, interviewer might just want to understand how you can tackle and understand the problem and approach it.
Even though it is very basic algorithm but it can be a possible answer to a vague question.


```
// Online Java Compiler
